text: Zhantoro Zholdoshevich Satybaldiyev (; born 6 January 1956) is a Kyrgyz politician. He was the 15th Prime Minister of Kyrgyzstan from 5 September 2012 until 25 March 2014. == References == == Other websites == * Sputnik.kg Category:1956 births Category:Living people Category:Prime Ministers of Kyrgyzstan
